@{
    Layout = null;
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Không có quyền truy cập - RaceMS</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/site.css" asp-append-version="true" />
    <style>
        @@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap');

        html, body { height: 100%; margin: 0; }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 20%, rgba(220,38,38,.15), transparent 40%),
                        linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 55%, #0f3460 100%);
            padding: 1.5rem;
        }

        .forbidden-card {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,.04);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 3rem 2.5rem;
            max-width: 460px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(0,0,0,.4);
        }

        .forbidden-icon { font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }

        .forbidden-card h1 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin: 0 0 .6rem;
        }

        .forbidden-card p {
            color: #a5b4d4;
            font-size: .9rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0 0 1.8rem;
        }

        .btn-back-login {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed, #6d28d9);
            color: #fff;
            font-size: .9rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 11px 26px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(109,40,217,.35);
            transition: all .2s;
        }

        .btn-back-login:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6d28d9, #5b21b6);
            color: #fff;
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="forbidden-card">
        <div class="forbidden-icon">🚫</div>
        <h1>Bạn không có quyền truy cập</h1>
        <p>Tài khoản hiện tại không đủ quyền để xem trang này. Nếu bạn cho rằng đây là nhầm lẫn, hãy liên hệ quản trị viên.</p>
        <a asp-action="Index" asp-controller="JockeyNguyenDnts" class="btn-back-login">← Quay lại trang chính</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
